---
import aboutmeImg from "/assets/aboutImg.webp";
import vsCode from "/assets/vscode.svg";
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <h2 class="about__title">Qui suis-je ?</h2>
  <div class="about__content">
    <div class="about__content__illustration">
      <img class="about__content__illustration__img" src={aboutmeImg} />
    </div>
    <div class="about__content__aside">
      <div class="about__content__aside__window">
        <div class="about__content__aside__window__header">
          <img
            class="about__content__aside__window__header__vscode"
            src={vsCode}
          />
          <p>whoAmI.js</p>
          <div class="about__content__aside__window__header__icons">
            <i class="fas fa-window-minimize" style="color: #8b949e;"></i>
            <i class="fa-sharp fa-regular fa-square" style="color: #8b949e;"
            ></i>
            <i class="fas fa-xmark" style="color: #8b949e;"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about__content__aside__window__content">
          <p class="about__content__aside__window__content__line1">
            <span class="color1">let</span><span class="color2">
              whoAmI</span
            ><span class="color3"> =</span>
          </p>
          <p class="about__content__aside__window__content__string">
            "Architecte en devenir de l'innovation, je suis constamment à la
            recherche de nouvelles idées pour rendre mes projets plus intuitifs
            et inspirants. Aujourd'hui j'écris ces lignes, afin de décrocher
            l'opportunité qui me permettra de bâtir des ponts entre les
            technologies émergentes et les besoins des utilisateurs. Pour moi,
            chaque projet mérite d'être une véritable symphonie d'innovation.
            <br />
            <br />
            Pablo, enchanté."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a
        class="about__content__aside__download"
        href="/Portfolio/assets/cv_pablo_sagnes.pdf"
        download="CV Pablo SAGNES"
        >Télécharger mon CV<i class="fa-solid fa-circle-down"></i></a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global lang="scss">
  .about__content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;

    &__illustration {
      position: relative;
      width: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 3em;
      opacity: 0;
      right: 500px;
      transition: 1.5s ease-in-out;
      @media only screen and (max-width: 900px) {
        display: none;
      }
      &__img {
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: contain;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }

    &__aside {
      width: 50%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      @media only screen and (max-width: 900px) {
        width: 100%;
      }

      &__window {
        position: relative;
        border: 1px solid #dfdfdf;
        align-self: center;
        height: fit-content;
        min-height: 20em;
        max-height: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        transform: scale(0);
        animation-name: pop-up;
        animation-duration: 0.7s;
        animation-delay: 3.5s;
        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
        transform-origin: bottom right;
        box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px;
        transition: 0.5s ease-in-out;

        &__header {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: space-between;
          padding: 0 10px;
          border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
          height: 30px;
          border-bottom: #dfdfdf 1px solid;
          background-color: #f8f8f8;

          & > * {
            max-height: 100%;
          }

          &__vscode {
            height: 80%;
          }
        }

        &__content {
          padding: 2em;

          &__string {
            color: #ac1515;
          }
        }
      }
      &__download {
        display: flex;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: clamp(250px, 90vw, 300px);
        border: 3px solid #3e64ff;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #3e64ff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-top: 4rem;
        height: 5rem;
        transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;

        &:hover {
          color: white;
          background: #3e64ff;
        }
        & i {
          margin-left: 2rem;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .color1 {
    color: #3e64ff;
  }

  .color2 {
    color: #403677;
  }

  .color3 {
    color: #001090;
  }

  .color4 {
    color: #ac1515;
  }
</style>
